WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.267 --> 00:00:12.901
Since 2011/2554, Tata Motors Thailand began to introduce tractor trucks 
from Tata Daewoo Commercial Vehicle (South Korea)

00:00:14.034 --> 00:00:18.934
Optimum truck NOVUS, the company introduced here for nearly 4 years

00:00:19.934 --> 00:00:24.434
But now for the occasion of this snake year's Bus &amp; Truck event at BITEC Bangna

00:00:24.934 --> 00:00:29.367
Tata introduces an entirely new and unique CV product yet to Thailand

00:00:43.634 --> 00:00:48.134
All-new Prima, a whole new series production from Tata Daewoo

00:00:48.967 --> 00:00:54.334
Known as the first ever European-styled truck, of both Tata Daewoo brand and South Korea

00:01:03.334 --> 00:01:08.234
Surprisingly still looking fresh through the seeming opposites, compromises, and tests

00:01:08.867 --> 00:01:14.167
With outstanding performance and operating, 
perhaps than any Tata Daewoo previously built

00:01:14.167 --> 00:01:18.000
Longer lifecycle and so higher impressive reliability

00:01:18.334 --> 00:01:22.167
Tata Thailand decided to import this LX 4028.S SR

00:01:22.201 --> 00:01:26.434
The 6-wheeler sleeper-cabin tractor truck (6x4), with single reduction rear axle

00:01:26.567 --> 00:01:30.667
Imported from the assembly plant in India instead of Korea

00:01:31.167 --> 00:01:35.267
Red exterior paint, with reflective stickers by 3M

00:01:35.901 --> 00:01:40.000
Recruited with top quality truck parts/components

00:02:01.067 --> 00:02:05.801
Aimed for easier driving and service/maintenance, as well as more road-time

00:02:06.334 --> 00:02:10.434
Powered by Cummins ISBe-270 6.7L Inline-6 Turbo-charged Diesel engine

00:02:10.501 --> 00:02:14.167
High-pressure Common-rail Fuel Injection Pump

00:02:14.267 --> 00:02:18.367
266HP (198kw) @ 2,500rpm, with 970 Newton-metre torque (@ 1,200-1,700rpm)

00:02:18.367 --> 00:02:21.967
Operating under the Bharat Stage III emission norm

00:02:22.601 --> 00:02:26.567
Mated with Tata's G1150 OD 9-speed (8F + 1Cr + 1R)

00:02:26.834 --> 00:02:29.801
With dry friction single disc clutch (430mm)

00:02:30.734 --> 00:02:33.501
400 litre fuel capacity

00:02:37.367 --> 00:02:41.000
Fully reinforced chassis and suspension

00:02:41.334 --> 00:02:44.967
Featuring RA110 single reduction rear axle (5.84 ratio)

00:02:45.434 --> 00:02:49.067
Front: Parabolic Leaf (90mm width)

00:02:49.501 --> 00:02:53.134
Rear: Semi-elliptical Multi Leaf Spring (90mm width)

00:02:53.767 --> 00:02:57.401
Wheels and tyres: 10R20-16PR

00:03:00.067 --> 00:03:04.234
Cabin and frame/chassis surpassed all the safety tests

00:03:04.301 --> 00:03:08.467
And has met the requirements of safety regulations worldwide

00:03:10.967 --> 00:03:15.134
As well as deceleration, with its Full Air S-Cam Dual Circuited Anti-lock Brake System

00:03:15.201 --> 00:03:19.367
Reflective stickers for safety provided by 3M, applied on 3 sides of cabin

00:03:23.467 --> 00:03:27.801
Prima's cabin is the fully suspended 4-point mounted type, with great indeed visibility

00:03:30.901 --> 00:03:35.234
In here is definitely European-sense large truck interior

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:42.334
Perhaps this is one foremost and unique way of inner cabin design

00:03:43.501 --> 00:03:47.834
True that it's plain, but will be more capable to everyday use

00:03:50.534 --> 00:03:54.767
Tilt &amp; Telescopic steering wheel, with 12,900mm minimum turning radius

00:03:54.934 --> 00:03:59.167
Large Analog Instrument Cluster with Multi-info teller screen

00:04:07.934 --> 00:04:12.167
Still have air conditioning, despite some equipments maybe removed

00:04:25.434 --> 00:04:29.234
Designed for the driver to drive longer with less fatigue

00:04:29.234 --> 00:04:33.167
Seats and sleepers in here are cloth upholstery

00:04:43.034 --> 00:04:48.134
Turnaround time is always one essential part among others, 
in the field of transportation/logistics

00:04:48.134 --> 00:04:52.034
Then it needs economy and efficiency to ease this invest act

00:04:52.334 --> 00:04:56.234
The Prima is truly a product emerged by Tata Daewoo's tallest order yet

00:04:56.234 --> 00:05:00.201
To build the better best CVs that the world demands of

00:05:00.367 --> 00:05:05.201
And it has already achieved the brand's own exceptional standards and requirements

00:05:06.167 --> 00:05:11.067
All this, so it is no wonder that this Tata Daewoo product is built by the Way of the World Class

00:05:11.067 --> 00:05:15.967
That will make a whole new experience of trucking, uniquely unlike any other

